title: Harry Potter - The Goblet Of Fire (Complete Audio Book)
description:
This is a complete copy of the audio book Harry Potter and The Goblet Of Fire. The files have been encoded in .AAC format at 64Kb/s and are directly ripped from the CDs. Due to the low complexity of the voice audio, high compression results in fantastic quality.

Album art has been added to each track and is optimized for playback in iTunes.

If you like my rip, then please seed it. Eventually the entire series will be posted, so please check back
